data.description: Stunning Craftsman style home located in the highly sought after Cresswell Subdivision and Peachtree Ridge school district!  This sizable home is an entertainers dream!  Featuring 5 bedrooms & 4 full bathrooms with 3,124 sq ft and a full unfinished terrace level that includes an additional 1,468 sq ft!  The main level features a separate dining/living room, beautiful open concept kitchen with granite countertops, gas range, eat in kitchen, spacious family room and a bedroom with a full bathroom.  Upstairs includes 4 additional bedrooms and 3 full bathrooms and loft area!  Located close to so many amazing restaurants, shopping, downtown Duluth, and easy access to I-85!  Only 7 years old and even includes a 1-year home warranty!  Don't miss out on the chance to make this your home!
